 ▼ hsiheader
 hsiheader.hThis is the main header file which is exported to the application developers. This can be used in conjunction with the mmWave SDK CBUFF driver to create a header which can then be attached to a data stream
 hsiprotocol.hThe header file exposes the HSI header and associated definitions. HSI headers are created and attached to an LVDS stream which is being transmitted. The headers can be decoded on the peer where the stream is received to get access to the actual data
